results.deck: Founded in 1994 and based in Gifu Prefecture, Japan, Nippon Ich release SRPG's. They found fame outside Japan with the release in the U.S. and Europe of Disgaea. Their most recent release being Z.H.P: Unlosing Ranger v.s Darkdeath Evilman for the PSP.
